DATA NOTICE

The MIT licence above covers the software (code) in this repository only.

The village map drawings displayed in the app are the work of Dr A Colin Day
(colinday.co.uk) and are made freely available for copying without charge.
They are not covered by the MIT licence.

The maps are derived from Ordnance Survey data.
Contains OS data © Crown copyright and database rights 2024.
Licensed under the Open Government Licence v3.0.
See https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/doc/open-government-licence/

The house coordinates in docs/houses.json were derived by the author from
personal observation of Esri World Imagery satellite imagery and are original
work of the author. This coordinate dataset (the hand-placed latitude/longitude
and drawing-pixel positions, in docs/houses.json and data/placements/) is
licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
Licence (CC BY-SA 4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

You may copy, share and adapt it, including for commercial use, provided you
credit "Adam Dent, Whereabouts (whereabouts-app.pages.dev)" and release any
adapted dataset under the same licence. This covers the coordinate data only,
not Colin Day's map drawings (see above), which carry their own terms.

This application is a navigation aid only. It is not a clinical tool and
must not be used as a substitute for clinical judgement. Coordinates may be
inaccurate. Always verify your destination before visiting.
